items.badge_description: Pucker up! The fourth in our series of “Super Style” badges, this one celebrates fruited sour ales, which ranked as the 4th most checked-in style of 2021. AVAILABLE ONLY TO UNTAPPD INSIDERS.

Let’s raise a glass to draft! Steel kegs are the most reusable container in the beer world, saving 6 BILLION single-use containers from waste streams each year. Congrats on grabbing a pint and helping us save the planet one tasty beverage at a time!

It’s been a long day and now it’s time for a reward. Crisp, tasty and refreshing, enjoy that delicious fruit beer! That's 500 different beers with the style of Fruit Beer, Sour - Smoothie / Pastry, or Sour - Fruited (Gose or Berliner Weisse). You have reached the top!!
Happy Untappd anniversary to you! Thanks for sticking around and drinking socially with us. Cheers! That's 7 years on Untappd!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 400 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 81!

It’s been a long day and now it’s time for a reward. Crisp, tasty and refreshing, enjoy that delicious fruit beer! That's 35 different beers with the style of Fruit Beer, Sour - Smoothie / Pastry, or Sour - Fruited (Gose or Berliner Weisse). Try 5 more for Level 8!

Right about now you’re feeling your face tighten and your taste buds explode. The full pucker is quickly setting in and you can’t get enough. This is the wonder of the sour. That's 105 different Sour Beers. Try 5 more for Level 22.

It’s been a long day and now it’s time for a reward. Crisp, tasty and refreshing, enjoy that delicious fruit beer! That's 80 different beers with the style of Fruit Beer, Sour - Smoothie / Pastry, or Sour - Fruited (Gose or Berliner Weisse). Try 5 more for Level 17!
